<div class=3D"ws-info">
  <p>Dijkstra's shortest path algorithm was invented in 1956 by the Dutch c=
omputer scientist Edsger W. Dijkstra during a twenty minutes coffee break, =
while out shopping with his fianc=C3=A9e in Amsterdam.</p>
  <p>The reason for inventing the algorithm was to test a new computer call=
ed ARMAC.</p>
