<h2>Dijkstra's Algorithm</h2>
<p>Dijkstra's algorithm finds the shortest path from one vertex to all othe=
r vertices.</p>
<p>It does so by repeatedly selecting the nearest unvisited vertex and calc=
ulating the distance to all the unvisited neighboring vertices.</p>
