ion">,</span> inf<span class=3D"token punctuation">,</span> inf<span class=
=3D"token punctuation">,</span> <span class=3D"token number">0</span><span =
class=3D"token punctuation">,</span> inf<span class=3D"token punctuation">,=
</span> inf<span class=3D"token punctuation">,</span> inf<span class=3D"tok=
en punctuation">]</span>
<span class=3D"token comment">#vertices   [ A ,  B ,  C , D,  E ,  F ,  G ]=
</span>
</code></pre>
</div>
