rtices A and E is infinite, the new distance to these are updated with the =
edge weights. So vertex A gets the distance changed from inf to 4, and vert=
ex E gets the distance changed to 2. As mentioned on the previous page, upd=
ating the distance values in this way is called 'relaxing'.</p>
