<p>The distance to all adjacent and not previously visited vertices from ve=
rtex E must now be calculated, and updated if needed.</p>
<p>The calculated distance from D to vertex A, via E, is 2+4=3D6. But the c=
urrent distance to vertex A is already 4, which is lower, so the distance t=
o vertex A is not updated.</p>
