<h2>Dijkstra's Algorithm on Directed Graphs</h2>
<p>To run Dijkstra's algorithm on directed graphs, very few changes are nee=
ded.</p>
<p>Similarly to the change we needed for <a href=3D"https://www.w3schools.c=
